There are currently 3 Summer internships available in the group funded via the Faraday institution [FUSE](https://faraday.ac.uk/opportunities/summer-internships/) program.  

- [Investigation on the Structure and Na Ion Transport Mechanisms in Na4MnV(PO4)3](https://www.bath.ac.uk/jobs/Vacancy.aspx?ref=CC7634)
- [Exploring the link between the Madelung potential and disorder in lithium rich cathode materials](https://www.bath.ac.uk/jobs/Vacancy.aspx?ref=CC7632)
- [Role of cation identity on local order in Li2MOS antiperovskite cathode materials](https://www.bath.ac.uk/jobs/Vacancy.aspx?ref=CC7633)
